name: Gift card £50
description:
The perfect gift for when you can't decide. This gift card is worth
£50 and can be used on anything in my shop.
The recipient will have to subscribe to my special gift card holders' mailing list (all instructions will come with the card), as these will receive a priority preview and an option to reserve before items go public. There will be a limited amount of such gift cards released
each month, so my planned monthly shop updates will still give a fair chance to both, card holders and general customers, to find something they'd like to purchase.

You will receive a paper gift card in the mail, wrapped up and ready
to give! Enclosed with your card, you will find easy to follow
instructions on how to subscribe to the above mentioned mailing list
and how to apply your card's value towards your order. A personal note from you(optional).

If your order total is more than your gift certificate value, you will
be sent a PayPal invoice for the difference.

If you do not use the entire balance, I will send you an email letting you know the remaining balance, which you can use at a later time.

This gift card is GBP, non-transferable, non-refundable, and has no cash value. 

If ordering via PayPal, please specify "to and from" in the comments
box, else please email me that information. If you'd like your order to be shipped directly to the recipient - please verify shipping
address in the notes box as well. If you are purchasing multiple gift
certificates for multiple gifts or people, please specify which
gift/person is related to which gift card.

Want an amount not listed? I can set up a custom listing for you to order a gift card with the amount you'd like.

Card ships within 24-48 hours.
